          "activation_name": "Path of the Pegasus",
          "activation_time": "10 minutes",
          "effect": "The *sacred valkyrie helm* casts *interplanar teleport* to your specifications. When you start this activation, each creature you target with this spell mounts a conjured pegasus who then carries them through reality to arrive at the specified location; each affected creature experiences the 10-minute activation as a kaleidoscopic ride through strange worlds and realities atop a pegasus\u2019s back.",
